         <div xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288"><!-- p3l6-r9 -->
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-Hd1e108"> ¶ De iteratione sermonis 
               vitanda. Rubrica 9</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-d1e114"> 
       <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-Rd1e112">IEsus filius sirach in ecclesiast.
      c. 7.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-Qd1e120">Non interes 
               sermonem in tua oratione.</quote> 
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-d1e126"> 
             / <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-Rd1e125">c. 42.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-Qd1e128">Non
        duplices sermonem.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-d1e134">
               ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-Rd1e137">Gaufridus in poetria. c. 41.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-Qd1e138">Respuat 
               audiri bis idem.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-d1e145">
               ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-Rd1e149">De multiplicatione verborum.
         <!--S missing--><sic>Alomon</sic> in prouerbiis
        c. 10.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-Qd1e149">In 
               multiloquio non deest peccatum.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-d1e159">
               ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-Rd1e170">Aristotelis retho. li. 3. et fi. c 18.</ref>
         <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-Qd1e163">Oportet non prolixe narrare: sicut neque 
               prohemizare prolixe: neque persuasiones dicere.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-d1e171">
               ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-Rd1e184">Oratius in poetria:</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-Qd1e175">Quicquid precipies
        esto breuis: vt cito dicta
        Percipiant animi dociles teneantque fideles
        Omne superuacuum pleno de pectore manat.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-d1e185">
               ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-Rd1e200">Tullius retho. artis vereris: li. i. c. 10.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-Qd1e189">
               Sepe res parum est intellecta longitudine 
               magis quam obscuritate narrationis.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-d1e197"> 
             / <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-Rd1e212">11. c.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-Qd1e199">
               Breuitas orationis est cum nisi necessarium 
               nullum assumitur verbum.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-d1e207"> 
             / <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-Rd1e224">14. c. et fi.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-Qd1e209">
               Commotis animis diutius in conquestione morari
        non oportebit. Quemadmodum enim 
               dixit Appolius retho. Lachryma nihil citius
        arescit.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-d1e222"> 
             / <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-Rd1e240">Idem retho. artis noue: lib. i. c. 5.</ref>
         <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-Qd1e224">Quo breuior eo lucidior et cognita facilior
        narratio est.</quote> 
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-d1e251">
             / <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-Rd1e253">Li. 2. c. 7.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-Qd1e255">Conmiserationem
        breuem esse oportet: nihil enim lachryma
        citius arescit.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-d1e236"> 
             / <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-Rd1e265">Idem de iure ciuili et 
               iustitia naturali: siue de legibus. l. iii.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-Qd1e238">Breuitas 
        <!--202.xml-->
        <cb ed="#V" n="b"/>
                  magna laus est in sententia: nec est vnquam 
               longa oratione vtendum.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-d1e282">
        ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-Rd1e286">Lex cod. ti. de veteri iure enucleando. li. ii.</ref>
         <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-Qd1e290">Multo vtilius pauca indonee effundere quam
        multis inutilibus homines pregrauari.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-d1e259">
               ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-Rd1e300">Priscianus in prohemio:</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-Qd1e263">In magna 
               operis materia impossibile est aliquid 
               perfectum breuiter exponi.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-d1e271"> 
             / <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-Rd1e312">Li. 7. ti. de 
               vocatiuo singulari sede declinationis:</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-Qd1e273">Iuniores
        breuitate gaudent.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-d1e281">
               ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-Rd1e327">Gregorius in pastorali. c. 16.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-Qd1e285">Sepe 
               dictorum virtus perditur: cum apud corda 
               audientium loquacitas incauta opportunitateleuigatur.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-d1e293">
               ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-Rd1e342">Isydorus soliloquiorum: li. 2. c. 13.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-Qd1e297">
               Tolle verbositatem sermonis superflui. 
               Multiloquium non effugiet culpam. Breuem 
               sermonem scientia facit.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-d1e308">
               ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-Rd1e358">Mattheus <sic>vintoniensis</sic> in poetria partur.
        i. c. 8.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-Qd1e312">Prolixitas nouerca est memorie.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-d1e318"> 
             / <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-Rd1e371">9.
        c.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-Qd1e320">Breuitas sibi aperta sibi amicat audatiam.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-d1e380">
         <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-Rd1e384">10. c.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-Qd1e386">Uerborum confusio nouerca est 
               intelligentie: et doctrine pretendit offendi 
               cultum. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-d1e332"> 
             / <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-Rd1e396">22. c.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-Qd1e334">Prolixitas fastidii puerpera
        est.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-d1e340"> 
             / <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-Rd1e406">Partur. 2. c. 3.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-Qd1e342">Infinitas nouerca est 
               discipline et amica confusionis.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-d1e348">
               ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-Rd1e419">Iacobus beneuentanus. c. 5. 7. et pe.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-Qd1e352">
               Inuidiam generat et longus tedia sermo.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-d1e358">
               ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-Rd1e431">Iudex venusinus: li. de pertractatione nuptis.
        c. i.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-Qd1e362">Sermo breuis longo gratior esse solet.</quote>
            </p>
         </div>
